result_0:
 In this challenge, you are required to write a function that takes an integer as input and returns the sum of all numbers from 1 to n. Here is a simple solution using a loop:

```php
function sumToN($n) {
    $sum = 0;
    for ($i = 1; $i <= $n; $i++) {
        $sum += $i;
    }
    return $sum;
}
```

This function iterates from 1 to n, adding each number to the sum variable. The final value of the sum is returned as the result.

